OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally overcast, with early
OL,6,Fhill fog gradually lifting, although
OL,7,Flimited bright or sunny intervals may
OL,8,Feventually develop for eastern areas.
OL,9,FThe cloud will be thick enough to
OL,10,Fbring patchy light rain and drizzle at
OL,11,Ftimes, most likely across western
OL,12,Fareas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FPredominantly dry and
OL,15,Fovercast, with hill fog gradually
OL,16,Fdeveloping. However, some clear
OL,17,Fintervals may occur across eastern
OL,18,Fareas, whilst further west there is a
OL,19,Fchance of occasional patchy light rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
