OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FMainly dry and overcast at
OL,6,Ffirst, with hill fog. Through the day
OL,7,Fbrighter conditions gradually develop,
OL,8,Fand sunny spells develop for many
OL,9,Fareas leading to above average
OL,10,Ftemperatures occurring.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fovercast with patchy drizzle and early
OL,14,Fhill fog. Tuesday becoming brighter
OL,15,Fwith perhaps showers arriving.
OL,16,FWednesday breezy with sunshine and
OL,17,Fscattered showers. Temperatures close
OL,18,Fto or slightly above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
